https://nginx.org/ru/
-
- Restart:
systemctl restart nginx
service nginx restart
- Config renew
nginx -s reload
- Test
nginx -t
- Show all nginx modules
strings /usr/sbin/nginx|grep _module|grep -v configure| sort
